summary: Improves the dorm given to you when you join the College of Winterhold.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=15][u]College of Winterhold Dorm Improvements[/u][/size]

This mod removes fur carpets and barrels and adds new wall mounted animal trophies. New to 1.1 a bookshelf and shelf.

This is my very first mod and I am only doing this for my personal learning processes. I know it is not the best mod but hopefully my mods will be gradually improving.

[size=10][u]To-Do[/u][/size]
[list] [*]Fix bookshelf bug [/list]

[size=10][u] Change-log[/u][/size]
[list] [*]1.1---Added shelf and bookshelf
[*]1.0---Initial Release [/list]
[/center]
